<CENTER><H3>Last Release: 2010-05-27</H3></CENTER>

<P CLASS=DESC>Current firmware, schematics, additional infos are located at <A HREF="midibox_seq.html">http://www.uCApps.de/midibox_seq.html</A>.</P>

