<LI><I>V4.0beta20</I>
  <UL>
  <LI> taken over track/layer button/LED usage of MBSEQ V3 (important if you are
    using the old frontpanel):
    <UL CLASS=CL>
    <LI> pattern page: track buttons have the same function like group buttons.<BR>
